START
  ↓
Initialize Sensors & Motors
  ↓
Read Distance from Ultrasonic Sensor
  ↓
Is Distance < Threshold?
   ↓ YES                      ↓ NO
Stop Vehicle              Move Forward
Turn Left/Right
  ↓
Send Data to Backend (WiFi)
  ↓
Backend Stores Data
  ↓
Frontend Fetches Data
  ↓
Display Live Status
  ↓
User Sends Control Command?
   ↓ YES → Send to Backend → Vehicle Executes
   ↓ NO
  ↓
Repeat Loop
